data.description: Welcome to Market 632 Pettit Rd. Pocahontas , Arkansas within the Pocahontas School District. If quaint country living is calling your name, then this 4 +/- acre treelined property is the one you've been waiting for. Nestled among mature shade trees is a Ranch style home with a covered porch The interior holds 1156 sf of well laid out living space over a split floor plan that contains: a large eat in kitchen with a dining area off the kitchen, living room, the Master bedroom with en-suite and large walk-in closet. The other two bedrooms are very spacious with nice closet space. This home a unfinished walk out basement that could be turned into a bonus rooms or for extra storage. The Seller loves the private yard full of wildlife such as deer, squirrel, foxes, and rabbit. Utilities include Propone, electric, well water, and septic .Conveniently located off of Highway 166 with close proximity to favorite local amenities. Call today to schedule your tour and make this house your home.
